ISic003070_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003070.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo R.J.A. Wilson\" src=\"ISic003070-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003070_detail_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo R.J.A. Wilson\" src=\"ISic003070_detail_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003070_detail.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo R.J.A. Wilson\" src=\"ISic003070_detail-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text from photograph</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 39.1005 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 34.0955 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Di Stefano 1984 175 no.191 ph <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002035\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002035</a>  </li><li> Manni Piraino 1987 25-26 tav.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001766\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001766</a>  </li><li> Vento 2000 54-56 tav.8-9 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001525\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001525</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Neatly painted square letters with short serifs, painted in the style of stone cut letters. Alpha is broad with straight bar; Epsilon has equal length horizontal strokes; theta is ovoid with a full horizontal bar; kappa has arms that are not quite ful length; mu has vertical first and last, with middle strokes nearly reaching down to the line; pi has equal length verticals; sigma is four-bar, of equal length, top and bottom strokes horizontal.</p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence </div>",
